    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "There have been many tears along with many fears"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Since I wandered away from my Father."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "I am a prodigal with a living abysmal,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Since I wandered away from my Father."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "What am I doing here? Stuck in want, without cheer,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "I am wasting away from my Father."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Back home all are well fed—everyone abounds in bread—"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "From the wealth in the house of my Father."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Though I went far abroad, sinned against man and God,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "I desire to return to my Father!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "I am now coming home, nevermore again to roam."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "I am coming back home to my Father!"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Still a long way off, I look up—to my surprise—"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "There is my Father running to meet me!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Then on my neck he falls, and despite all my shortfalls,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "He starts to kiss me affectionately."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "I regret all I’ve done; I’m an unworthy son,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Yet my dear Father is full of mercy!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "The best robe He gives me… a ring… sandals for my feet;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "And He feeds me—I’m no longer hungry!"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Oh what joy to be here! Back with my Father dear!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "I am no longer far from my Father!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Father, how I love You!  And I know You love me too."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Here in Your house I will dwell forever!"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
